  "description": {
    "zh": "\"狩猎愉快\"。这正是我表兄借给我他的霰弹枪让我往桌上添点食物时告诉我的。但现在不是沉浸在怀旧中的时候！我们可以留到另一个时间……也许。\n\n嗯 then……我刚刚说到哪了？哦，对了，你的任务。又是霰弹枪，对吧？太棒了。你将能享受到一些更有趣的武器，我可以给你这把美国造的，它超级贵，所以我建议你别弄丢了。明白吗？我甚至不确定经销商们是否有库存，可能没有。毕竟我们不得不追捕几个军火贩子才弄到它们。\n\n好了，我不再“闲聊废话”了，你真没礼貌……给，清单也拿着，做完就回来，你知道吗？这把霰弹枪你留着吧。",
    "en": "\"Happy Hunting\". That is exactly what I've been told when my cousin lent me his shotgun to put some food on the table. But now is not the time to drown in nostalgia! We can save that for another time... Maybe.\n\nWell then... Where was I again? Oh, yeah, your task. Shotguns again, right? Fantastic. You'll be able to enjoy some more interesting weapons, I can give you this american-made one, it's super expensive so I suggest you don't lose it. Got it? I'm not even sure if anyone of the dealers has them in stock, probably not. After all we had to chase down a few gunrunners for them.\n\nAlright, I'll quit \"chatting nonsense\", so rude of you... Here, have the list aswell, come back when you're done, and you know what? Keep the shotgun."
  },
